data.title: Serena Bright Mammography Machine
data.meta_description: Serena Bright makes it possible to clearly target lesions enhancing with contrast spectral mammography. Leverage the Pristina Serena ease of use with no additional hardware added. Easy scheduling and familiar setting for your patient vs MRI-guided biopsy.
data.text: GE HealthCare continues to innovate and improve the mammography experience through Senographe Pristina and supporting products for imaging review, biopsy, and contrast-enhanced mammography.
